{"id":441,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":43,"title":"43. Can I Let You Know?","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":18,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know.441/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/0-43-can-i-let-you-know.mp3","transcript":"Are you going out with Leonard tonight?\nUh huh. He's supposed to pick me up at 6:30 What time is it now?\n5:45. You'd better get going.\nYou're kidding. I haven't even taken a shower.\nWhere are you going?\nWe haven't made up our minds yet. Maybe to a movie, maybe to a party.\nGo and see Forrest Gump. It's supposed to be interesting.\nOh, maybe we will. I've heard The Sixth Sense is good, too.\nWell, personally I prefer Forrest Gump.\nI really should be going. Do you wanna go shopping tomorrow?\nI'd like to go, but it depends.\nI might have to go to the store tomorrow and do some work.\nCan I let you know first thing in the morning?\nOK, that would be all right.\nOh, there's the phone. It must be Leonard.\nWell, I'll be going. Call me tomorrow.\nI will. Have a good evening.\nYou too.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:44","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Are you going out with Leonard tonight?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/1.mp3","time_start":2.13,"time_end":3.77},{"position":2,"content":"Uh huh. He's supposed to pick me up at 6:30 What time is it now?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/2.mp3","time_start":3.77,"time_end":6.87},{"position":3,"content":"5:45. You'd better get going.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/3.mp3","time_start":6.96,"time_end":8.91},{"position":4,"content":"You're kidding. I haven't even taken a shower.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/4.mp3","time_start":8.91,"time_end":10.98},{"position":5,"content":"Where are you going?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/5.mp3","time_start":11.02,"time_end":11.95},{"position":6,"content":"We haven't made up our minds yet. Maybe to a movie, maybe to a party.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/6.mp3","time_start":11.95,"time_end":15.19},{"position":7,"content":"Go and see Forrest Gump. It's supposed to be interesting.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/7.mp3","time_start":15.27,"time_end":18.44},{"position":8,"content":"Oh, maybe we will. I've heard The Sixth Sense is good, too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/8.mp3","time_start":18.89,"time_end":21.84},{"position":9,"content":"Well, personally I prefer Forrest Gump.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/9.mp3","time_start":21.96,"time_end":24.12},{"position":10,"content":"I really should be going. Do you wanna go shopping tomorrow?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/10.mp3","time_start":24.12,"time_end":26.75},{"position":11,"content":"I'd like to go, but it depends.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-03-07-21-19-14/11.mp3","time_start":26.75,"time_end":28.25},{"position":12,"content":"I might have to go to the store tomorrow and do some work.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/43-can-i-let-you-know-2022-